  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\n`genesis_time` is required to determine the present slot.\r\n\r\nPresently, the val client assumes that the `genesis_time` is known, this will not be the case whilst we're waiting for the deposit contract to fill up and emit a chain-start event.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\n- Implement some service that can poll the beacon node and determine (a) if a `genesis_time` exists and (b) what it is.",
