    "body": "I'm considering a service which is akin to an `info()`. This requests basic information from the beacon node, to initiate the validator client. Information would include, \r\n```\r\nversion, // beacon node version \r\nchain_id / network_id, \r\ngenesis_time, // possibly genesis_hash also, as we could hard-code known hashes for chains in the future for added security.\r\n... // maybe other things (no of peers maybe, validators might want to choose different nodes..)\r\n```\r\n",
